init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As he was about to head to the shower he noticed that all of his other mugs said "#56,743 Dad".

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He got dressed and headed off to work.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Jeff rolled down his windows to ask what was going on.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As he pulled into the parking lot of his office building he noticed that all of the cars had their windows down and coffee mugs out.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Jeff thought to himself that the prank was getting a little out of hand.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He entered the office and as he walked down the hall, he noticed that all of the doors were open and people where shouting about who was

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Everyone was stunned to see the Pope was a dad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So, if you are looking for a way to be a better dad, look no further than your mug.
